        "TileImage": "$($repository 1f6cbfc3-06d5-49b2-9eca-ca22bde2bbf3).Image",
        "Description": "Agent Crooks,\r\rThis contract has been activated by Twitch themselves.\r\rSomeone has acquired a very compromising video of you and have contacted Twitch in an attempt to bribe them, with the offset that they keep their favourite streamer in viewers high graces. Naturally Twitch have yet to respond to their emails, however instead have contacted you to take out this problem-maker.\r\rAs this is a Twitch sensitive matter, this must look like an accident, with no collateral damage.\r\rBest of luck Crooks",
